post_text:
Event Name: WNY Maple Festival SAPS Race
Date: Sunday, April 28th
Time: 9:00am
Location: Franklinville Jr./Sr. High School 31 North Academy Street Franklinville, NY 14737

Please join us on Sunday April 28, 2019 for the Western New York Maple Festival SAPS Race. A longstanding tradition as a part of the WNY Maple Festival, this is a 5K walk/run and 10K run sponsored by the Franklinville Central School Student Council. All proceeds go towards putting on the race, and towards Student Council. We are also asking that each participant donate a non-perishable food item(s) for the local food pantry.
Link for more information or to register online: https://wnymaplefest.itsyourrace.com/event.aspx?id=7011
Participants may also register by filling out a form at the High School office at Franklinville Central School.
#proudTBApanther

Need your help!
For the past ???? years we have decorated the gym in the elementary school like a town (Christmas Town) the week before break. We use play money and the kids are able to go around the town and ‚Äúbuy‚Äù things (toy store, pet shop, restaurant, sports store, car shop, gas station, clothing store etc).
